00:16:06.758 --> 00:16:08.009
What do you mean she can't talk?

264
00:16:08.426 --> 00:16:10.261
Is she can't talk
or she won't talk?

265
00:16:10.345 --> 00:16:11.429
<i>She said she's not talking</i>

266
00:16:11.513 --> 00:16:13.348
