271
00:16:21.064 --> 00:16:22.148
<i>Meyor Lasky?</i>

272
00:16:22.232 --> 00:16:23.733
It's okay. she'll know
who that is.

273
00:16:23.817 --> 00:16:26.903
And you tell her that Mr. Lansky

