447
00:25:49.674 --> 00:25:51.300
Then what line
of business are you in?

448
00:25:52.718 --> 00:25:54.136
Truck rentals.

449
00:25:54.220 --> 00:25:56.556
Truck rentals?
What does that mean?

450
00:25:56.931 --> 00:25:58.432
Means we rent trucks.

451
00:25:58.516 --> 00:26:00.977
Anne. look.

452
00:26:01.519 --> 00:26:04.564
